Summary:
When the user puts a released movie in favorites (i.e. The Godfather), the push notification is sent with the message: "The Godfather is about to hit theatres", even though movie is released years ago. This happens will all released movies, and not with Upcoming ones.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Click on Feed button on the bottom of screen.
2. Click on The Godfather movie in the Top rated movies category.
3. Press on the Heart button on the movie information screen.
Result: Push notification received.